{"tid":2442690,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"五大紀律部隊完成中式步操培訓 今舉行結業典禮","createTime":"2021-03-11T13:34:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T15:01:25.000Z","uid":285248,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"8aa1f8f659e527cbafb6f412ebc9a5b9077d7cde","tid":2442690,"uid":285248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:34:43.000Z","msg":"柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n//【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=XsjoyflP4JPXBkuZaWCkHSLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=f1d29e78\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】本港雖已回歸23年，惟政府官方儀式一直跟從英國殖民地時代的規定而行，本港各大紀律部隊至今仍使用英式步操。據了解，於上月22日起在香港警察學院舉行的中式隊列培訓班今（11日）完成，並舉行五大紀律部隊步操教官中式正步步操結業典禮，有近80名受訓學員參與。//<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ws26KyZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fws26KyZ.jpg&h=1b53f204&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BA%94%E5%A4%A7%E7%B4%80%E5%BE%8B%E9%83%A8%E9%9A%8A%E5%AE%8C%E6%88%90%E4%B8%AD%E5%BC%8F%E6%AD%A5%E6%93%8D%E5%9F%B9%E8%A8%93-%E4%BB%8A%E8%88%89%E8%A1%8C%E7%B5%90%E6%A5%AD%E5%85%B8%E7%A6%AE-105955360.html?ncid=facebook_hkfacebook_a19b6y3mefk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E4%25BA%2594%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%25B4%2580%25E5%25BE%258B%25E9%2583%25A8%25E9%259A%258A%25E5%25AE%258C%25E6%2588%2590%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25BC%258F%25E6%25AD%25A5%25E6%2593%258D%25E5%259F%25B9%25E8%25A8%2593-%25E4%25BB%258A%25E8%2588%2589%25E8%25A1%258C%25E7%25B5%2590%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E5%2585%25B8%25E7%25A6%25AE-105955360.html%3Fncid%3Dfacebook_hkfacebook_a19b6y3mefk&d=XsjoyflP4JPXBkuZaWCkHSLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=6179de30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BA%94%E5%A4%A7%E7%B4%80%E5%BE%8B%E9%83%A8%E9%9A%8A%E5%AE%8C%E6%88%90%E4%B8%AD%E5%BC%8F%E6%AD%A5%E6%93%8D%E5%9F%B9%E8%A8%93-%E4%BB%8A%E8%88%89%E8%A1%8C%E7%B5%90%E6%A5%AD%E5%85%B8%E7%A6%AE-105955360.htm